{"id":"guide/template-overview","title":"Understanding templates","contents":"\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/template-overview.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"understanding-templates\" translation-result=\"on\">瞭解範本<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-overview#understanding-templates\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\">Understanding templates<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-overview#understanding-templates\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在 Angular 中，範本是使用者介面 （UI） 片段的藍圖。範本是用 HTML 編寫的，可以在範本中使用特殊語法來建構 Angular 的許多特性。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">In Angular, a template is a blueprint for a fragment of a user interface (UI).  Templates are written in HTML, and special syntax can be used within a template to build on many of Angular's features.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\" translation-result=\"on\">前提條件<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-overview#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Prerequisites<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-overview#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在學習範本語法之前，你應該熟悉下列內容：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Before learning template syntax, you should be familiar with the following:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/architecture\">Angular 的概念</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/architecture\">Angular concepts</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>JavaScript</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>HTML</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>CSS</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"enhancing-html\" translation-result=\"on\">增強 HTML<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-overview#enhancing-html\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Enhancing HTML<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-overview#enhancing-html\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">Angular 使用額外的特性擴充了範本中的 HTML 語法。例如，Angular 的資料繫結語法有助於動態設定文件物件模型 （DOM） 屬性。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Angular extends the HTML syntax in your templates with additional functionality.<br>\nFor example, Angular’s data binding syntax helps to set Document Object Model (DOM) properties dynamically.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">幾乎所有 HTML 語法都是有效的範本語法。但是，由於 Angular 範本只是 UI 的一個片段，因此它不包含 <code>&lt;html&gt;</code> 、 <code>&lt;body&gt;</code> 或 <code>&lt;base&gt;</code> 等元素。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Almost all HTML syntax is valid template syntax.  However, because an Angular template is only a fragment of the UI, it does not include elements such as <code>&lt;html&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;body&gt;</code>, or <code>&lt;base&gt;</code>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"alert is-important\">\n<p translation-result=\"on\">為了消除指令碼注入攻擊的風險，Angular 不支援範本中使用 <code>&lt;script&gt;</code> 元素。Angular 會忽略 <code>&lt;script&gt;</code> 標記，並向瀏覽器控制檯輸出一條警告。欲知詳情，參閱<a href=\"guide/security\">“安全性”</a>頁面。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To eliminate the risk of script injection attacks, Angular does not support the <code>&lt;script&gt;</code> element in templates.  Angular ignores the <code>&lt;script&gt;</code> tag and outputs a warning to the browser console.\nFor more information, see the <a href=\"guide/security\">Security</a> page.</p>\n\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"more-on-template-syntax\" translation-result=\"on\">關於範本語法的更多資訊<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-overview#more-on-template-syntax\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">More on template syntax<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-overview#more-on-template-syntax\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">你可能還對下列內容感興趣：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">You might also be interested in the following:</p>\n\n<div class=\"card-container\">\n    <a href=\"guide/interpolation\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Interpolation\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">插值</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Interpolation</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">學習如何在 HTML 中使用插值和表示式。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to use interpolation and expressions in HTML.</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">插值</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Interpolation</p>\n    \n</a>\n<a href=\"guide/property-binding\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Property binding\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">屬性（Property）繫結</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Property binding</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">設定目標元素或指令中帶有 @Input() 裝飾器的屬性（Property） @Input()。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Set properties of target elements or directive @Input() decorators.</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">屬性（Property）繫結</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Property binding</p>\n    \n</a>\n<a href=\"guide/attribute-binding\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Attribute binding\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">屬性（Attribute）繫結</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Attribute binding</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">設定屬性（Attribute）的值。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Set the value of attributes.</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">屬性（Attribute）繫結</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Attribute binding</p>\n    \n</a>\n<a href=\"guide/class-binding\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Class and style binding\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">類和樣式繫結</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Class and style binding</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">設定類和樣式的值。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Set the value of class and style.</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">類和樣式繫結</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Class and style binding</p>\n    \n</a>\n<a href=\"guide/event-binding\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Event binding\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">事件繫結</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Event binding</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">監聽 HTML 事件。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Listen for events and your HTML.</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">事件繫結</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Event binding</p>\n    \n</a>\n<a href=\"guide/template-reference-variables\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Template reference variables\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">範本參考變數</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Template reference variables</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">在範本中使用特殊變數參考某個 DOM 元素。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use special variables to reference a DOM element within a template.</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">範本參考變數</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Template reference variables</p>\n    \n</a>\n<a href=\"guide/built-in-directives\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Built-in directives\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">內建指令</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Built-in directives</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">監聽並修改 HTML 的行為和佈局。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Listen to and modify the behavior and layout of HTML.</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">內建指令</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Built-in directives</p>\n    \n</a>\n<a href=\"guide/inputs-outputs\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Inputs and Outputs\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">輸入屬性與輸出屬性</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Inputs and Outputs</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">在父級上下文和子指令、子元件之間共享資料。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Share data between the parent context and child directives or components.</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">輸入屬性與輸出屬性</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Inputs and Outputs</p>\n    \n</a>\n</div>\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間：5/11/2022</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/template-reference-variables\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - guide/architecture\n - guide/attribute-binding\n - guide/built-in-directives\n - guide/class-binding\n - guide/event-binding\n - guide/inputs-outputs\n - guide/interpolation\n - guide/property-binding\n - guide/security\n - guide/template-overview#enhancing-html\n - guide/template-overview#more-on-template-syntax\n - guide/template-overview#prerequisites\n - guide/template-overview#understanding-templates\n - guide/template-overview#瞭解範本\n - guide/template-overview#關於範本語法的更多資訊\n - guide/template-overview#前提條件\n - guide/template-overview#增強-html\n - guide/template-reference-variables\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/template-overview.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n-->"}